    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/11452630665912179599" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Rachel</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2012/01/i-am-here-to-tell-you/#comment-35430"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2012-01-26T23:43:33-05:00">Thursday, January 26, 2012 at 11:43 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>YUM! Just made this, substituting almonds and some walnuts for the pecans and this is seriously one of the tastiest treats I&#39;ve ever put in my mouth.  Thank you!  </p>
<p>I agree on cutting back the brown sugar next time.  I added some dried cranberries after it came out of the oven and bam, perfect.</p>
    </div>

