      <p>I&#39;ve been making my own granola for a few years, and thought about using olive oil instead of veg but never dared (for no good reason). Now I have, and it is a game changer. Now, if it were just easier to get ahold of maple syrup in China (without making breakfast the most expensive meal of the day).</p>
