    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is THE STUFF. I have tried quite a few granola recipes in my time and never found one worth repeating, but I have a feeling I&#39;ll be making this one every week. B/c husband is allergic to tree nuts and I don&#39;t like making everything taste like peanuts, I skipped the nuts and added some crushed hemp seed and whole alfalfa seeds. Soooo yummy, and I am amazed that it doesn&#39;t taste like my fairly strong flavored olive oil?! Thank you for the recipe.</p>
